WEBVTT

00:01.238 --> 00:04.331
<i>"Dante, do not weep yet" Beatrice said.</i>

00:04.416 --> 00:11.323
<i>"Do not weep yet, for soon another wound shall
make you weep far more tears than those!"</i>

00:11.409 --> 00:13.497
<i>Dante Alighieri
"The Divine Comedy"</i>

