57:44.474 --> 57:47.320
<i>Pawel Wypych, Secretary of State</i>

57:47.528 --> 57:50.820
<i>Mariusz Hanzlik, Undersecretary of State</i>

57:51.028 --> 57:53.528
<i>Andrzej Kremer, Deputy Minister
of Foreign Affairs,</i>

57:53.736 --> 57:57.778
<i>Stanislaw Komorowski,
Ministry of National Defence,</i>

57:58.028 --> 58:00.403
<i>Tomasz Merta,
